    {
      "id": "l7-words",
      "type": "theory",
      "title": "Shopping and money words",
      "body": "# Shopping and money\n\nCore words for the shop:\n\n- **Shop** (दुकान) · **Money** (पैसा) · **Price** (कीमत)\n- **Cheap** (सस्ता) and **Expensive** (महँगा)\n- **Buy** (खरीदना) · **Sell** (बेचना) · **Pay** (भुगतान करना)\n\nIn English the price word comes **before** the noun: *a cheap shirt* (एक सस्ती क़मीज़), *an expensive phone* (एक महँगा फ़ोन). The word **cheap** or **expensive** never changes for gender."
    },
    {
